# Pricing & Business Model Analysis

## Executive Summary

The Canadian DEI consulting market demonstrates **significant pricing variation** based on service type, delivery model, firm size, and client segment. Mid-market pricing dominates, with premium specialization and low-cost volume as secondary strategies.

