## Pricing by Delivery Model

### In-Person Delivery

- **Average Engagement:** $25-50K
- **Duration:** 2-6 months
- **Margin:** 30-45%
- **Demand:** Stable declining (post-pandemic shift)
- **Premium Multiplier:** 1.5x vs. online

### Hybrid Delivery (In-person + Online)

- **Average Engagement:** $20-40K
- **Duration:** 3-9 months
- **Margin:** 35-50%
- **Demand:** Growing (42% of market)
- **Note:** Optimal balance of interaction + scalability

### Online/Virtual Delivery

- **Average Engagement:** $8-20K
- **Duration:** 1-3 months
- **Margin:** 25-40%
- **Demand:** Rapidly growing (32% of market)
- **Advantage:** Scalability, accessibility, lower cost

### Self-Service/Platform

- **Average Engagement:** $500-5K/year
- **Duration:** Continuous access
- **Margin:** 40-70%
- **Demand:** Emerging (5% of market)
- **Advantage:** Highest margins, minimal labor

