## Pricing Optimization Insights

### Premium Pricing Factors

**Justifies 40-50% price premium:**

1. **Specialization** — Deep expertise in specific domain (e.g., AI Ethics, neurodiversity)
1. **Proprietary Methodology** — Unique approach or assessment tool
1. **Measurable Outcomes** — Clear ROI metrics and accountability
1. **Thought Leadership** — Published research, speaking authority
1. **Executive Alignment** — C-suite engagement and sponsorship
1. **Industry Expertise** — Vertical specialization (tech, healthcare, finance)

### Margin Optimization Strategies

**High-Margin Plays:**

1. **Outcomes-Based Pricing** — Tie pricing to results (30-50% margins)
1. **Productization** — Convert services to scalable products/programs (40-60% margins)
1. **Technology Enablement** — Use tools to reduce labor intensity (45-70% margins)
1. **Specialization** — Focus on underserved niches with lower competition (35-50% margins)

**Margin Compression Risks:**

1. **Commoditization** — Generic training offering (10-20% margins)
1. **Scale-dependent Model** — Relies on volume not value (15-25% margins)
1. **Labor-Intensive Delivery** — High facilitation costs (20-30% margins)

